name: DailyGoat.com
description: Daily Goat is a Blockchain-powered news publication featuring not only the biggest news stories of the day in the best media but also stories from the world's leading journalists that they can't get published anywhere else due to media bias and the political agendas of modern newsrooms. It is published by international news agency NewsX. DailyGoat.com (DGC) is Daily Goat's official meme coin.
